meanings.definition: Velpen is a village in the Dutch province of Gelderland. It is located in the municipality of Rheden, about 5 km east of the town of Rheden.
meanings.english_definition: Velpen is a village in the Dutch province of Gelderland. It is located in the municipality of Rheden, about 5 km east of the town of Rheden.
